query:
INSERT INTO projects (
                organization_id,
                name,
                metadata
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3)
            RETURNING
                id               AS "id!: Uuid",
                organization_id  AS "organization_id!: Uuid",
                name             AS "name!",
                metadata         AS "metadata!: Value",
                created_at       AS "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
